statements.sql: select * from `admin_users` where `id` = 1 and `admin_users`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1

select `permissions`.*, `model_has_permissions`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_permissions`.`permission_id` as `pivot_permission_id`, `model_has_permissions`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `permissions` inner join `model_has_permissions` on `permissions`.`id` = `model_has_permissions`.`permission_id` where `model_has_permissions`.`model_id` = 1 and `model_has_permissions`.`model_type` = 'App\Models\AdminUser'

select `roles`.*, `model_has_roles`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_roles`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `model_has_roles`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` where `model_has_roles`.`model_id` = 1 and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\Models\AdminUser'

select `permissions`.*, `role_has_permissions`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `role_has_permissions`.`permission_id` as `pivot_permission_id` from `permissions` inner join `role_has_permissions` on `permissions`.`id` = `role_has_permissions`.`permission_id` where `role_has_permissions`.`role_id` in (1, 2)
select *, (select count(1) - 1 from `menu` as `_d` where `menu`.`lft` between `_d`.`lft` and `_d`.`rgt`) as `depth` from `menu` where `menu`.`id` = 0 limit 1

select (select count(1) from `menu` where (`lft` >= `rgt` or (`rgt` - `lft`) % 2 = 0)) as `oddness`, (select count(1) from `menu` as `c1`, `menu` `c2` where `c1`.`id` < `c2`.`id` and (`c1`.`lft`=`c2`.`lft` or `c1`.`rgt`=`c2`.`rgt` or `c1`.`lft`=`c2`.`rgt` or `c1`.`rgt`=`c2`.`lft`)) as `duplicates`, (select count(1) from `menu` as `c`, `menu` as `p`, `menu` as `i` where `c`.`parent_id`=`p`.`id` and `i`.`id` <> `p`.`id` and `i`.`id` <> `c`.`id` and (`c`.`lft` not between `p`.`lft` and `p`.`rgt` or `c`.`lft` between `i`.`lft` and `i`.`rgt` and `i`.`lft` between `p`.`lft` and `p`.`rgt`)) as `wrong_parent`, (select count(1) from `menu` where (`parent_id` is not null and not exists (select 1 from `menu` as `p` where `menu`.`parent_id` = `p`.`id` limit 1))) as `missing_parent` limit 1
